title: Tibetan Singing Bowl Set (Buddha Chakra carved) - in 4 colors
description:
Sound bowls (Singing bowls) are used in some Buddhist religious practices to accompany periods of
meditation and chanting. Struck and singing bowls are widely used for music making, healing,
meditation and relaxation, as well for personal spirituality. Size (Height x Diameter) & Weight
chart Small 2.1" x 3.6" 410g Medium 2.2" x 4.2" 613g Large 2.8" x 4.5" *approximately
